    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "professional help won't change the numbers. the debt is astronomical. it's not just some bad week, it's a total collapse of my entire life. i look at my kids and i just feel this massive wave of shame. they deserve a father who succeeded, not this wreck. it feels like there's no version of the future where this isn't just a permanent stain on them.",
